Package org.hibernate

Interface SharedSessionContract

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, QueryProducer, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EventSource, Session, SessionImplementor, SharedSessionContractImplementor, StatelessSession
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDelegateSessionImplementor, AbstractSharedSessionContract, SessionDelegatorBaseImpl, SessionImpl, SessionLazyDelegator, StatelessSessionImpl, ToOneDelegateSessionImplementor
    public interface SharedSessionContract
extends QueryProducer, Closeable, Serializable
    Declares operations that are common between Session and StatelessSession.
